roups|qq=}} containing one carbon atom, such as {{ill|methane|ja|メタン|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/methane|qq=}} and {{ill|methyl group|ja|メチル基|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/methyl group|qq=}}. * Its opposite counterpart is {{ill|Ki (己)|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki (己)|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}} (tsuchinoto). * The {{ill|lucky direction|ja|恵方|3=歳徳神|1=Toshitoku-shin|lt=Lucky direction|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/lucky direction|13=User:Immanuelle/Toshitoku-shin|qq=}} associated with Kō is slightly east of northeast (75 degrees).
