le/Yang Wood Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Dragon|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Wood Tiger|ja|1=Yang Wood Tiger|2=ja|甲寅|1=Yang Wood Tiger|2=ja|3=甲寅|zh|1=Yang Wood Tiger|2=ja|甲寅|1=Yang Wood Tiger|2=ja|3=甲寅|ko|갑인|fr|Tigre de bois|de|Holz-Tiger|en|Wood Tiger|lt=甲寅 (Yang Wood Tiger)|lt_ko=갑인|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Tiger|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Tiger|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Tiger|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Tiger|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Tiger|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Tiger|qq=}} |}
