=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, and in Japan, it is referred to as "{{ill|Kinoe (甲)|kinoe|ja|きのえ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}" (elder wood).
